System Management Application (SMA)\par
\pard\fs24\par
\pard\fi-360\li360\tx360 1.\tab M\u7909?\f2 c \'f0\'edch\par
\pard\li360\cf0\f3\fs22 Nh\'fd \'f0\f4\'e3 bi\u7871?t, vi\u7879?c qu\u7843?n tr\u7883? h\u7879? th\u7889?ng cho m\u7897?t \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng qu\u7843?n l\'fd th\'f4ng tin l\'e0 v\'f4 c\'f9ng ph\u7913?c t\u7841?\f3 p v\'e0 kh\'f3 kh\'e3n. Trong \'f0\'f3\f4  c\'f3 vi\u7879?c ph\'e2n quy\u7873?\f3 n cho ng\'fd\f4\u7901?i d\'f9ng \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng chi\u7871?m m\u7845?t kh\'e1 nhi\u7873?u c\'f4ng s\u7913?c v\'e0 th\u7901?i gian c\u7911?\f3 a ng\'fd\f4\u7901?i ph\'e1t tri\u7875?n \u7913?ng d\u7909?\f3 ng. H\'f5n n\f4\u7919?a, vi\u7879?c ph\'e1t tri\u7875?n \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng m\u7897?t c\'e1ch c\u7893?\f5  \'f0i\f4\u7875?\f3 n nh\'fd: G\'e1n c\f4\u7913?ng c\'e1c Menu tr\'ean m\u7897?t Form ch\'ednh khi\u7871?\f3 n cho ng\'fd\f4\u7901?i d\'f9ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875? t\'f9y bi\u7871?\f3 n v\'e0 \'f0i\f4\u7873?u ch\u7881?nh c\'e1c ch\u7913?\f5 c n\'e3ng theo nghi\f4\u7879?p v\u7909? ri\'eang c\u7911?a m\'ecnh \f5\'f0\'f4i l\'fac c\f4\u361?ng s\u7869? g\'e2y l\'ean s\u7921? \u7913?c ch\u7871?. Ch\'ednh v\'ec v\u7853?\f5 y, SMA \'f0\f4\'e3 \f3\'f0\'fd\f4\u7907?c thi\u7871?t k\u7871?\f5  ra \'f0\f4\u7875? gi\'fap cho c\'e1c nh\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\u7875?n \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng qu\u7843?n l\'fd th\'f4ng tin b\u7857?\f3 ng CNTT \'f0\'fd\f4\u7907?c d\u7877?\f3  d\'e0ng h\'f5n. \f4\par
V\u7899?\f3 i SMA, ng\'fd\f4\u7901?i ph\'e1t tri\u7875?n kh\'f4ng c\u7847?n quan t\'e2\f5 m \'f0\f4\u7871?n vi\u7879?c ph\u7843?i x\'e2y d\u7921?ng m\u7897?t h\u7879? th\u7889?ng ph\'e2n quy\u7873?n ph\u7913?c t\u7841?p, c\u361?\f3 ng nh\'fd kh\'f4ng c\f4\u7847?n ph\u7843?\f5 i quan t\'e2m \'f0\f4\u7871?n giao di\u7879?n c\u7911?\f3 a ch\'fd\'f5ng tr\f4\'ecnh m\'e0 ch\u7881? c\u7847?\f5 n quan t\'e2m \'f0\f4\u7871?n vi\u7879?c ph\'e1t tri\u7875?n c\'e1c l\'f5i(DLL) cho \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng c\u7911?a m\'ecnh. Sau \f5\'f0\'f3, b\f4\u7857?\f3 ng SMA ng\'fd\f4\u7901?i ph\'e1t tri\u7875?n s\u7869?\f3  khai b\'e1o v\'e0 \'f0\'fda nh\f4\u7919?ng g\'ec m\'ecnh ph\'e1t tri\u7875?\f3 n \'f0\'fd\f4\u7907?c v\'e0 SMA s\u7869? bi\u7871?n n\'f3 tr\u7903? th\'e0nh \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng th\u7921?c ti\u7877?n.\par
SMA th\u7921?c s\u7921? l\'e0 m\u7897?t c\'f4ng c\u7909? m\u7841?nh m\u7869? v\'e0 kh\u7843? chuy\u7875?\f5 n, linh \'f0\f4\u7897?ng v\'e0 hi\u7879?u qu\u7843?\'85X\u7913?\f5 ng \'f0\'e1ng tr\f4\u7903? th\'e0nh m\u7897?t ph\u7847?n kh\'f4ng th\u7875? thi\u7871?u trong c\'e1c \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng qu\u7843?\f5 n l\'fd th\'f4ng tin \'f0\f4\u7889?i v\u7899?i c\'e1c nh\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\u7875?n \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng. N\'f3 s\u7869? gi\'fap cho m\u7897?t \u7913?ng d\u7909?\f5 ng \'f0\f4\'e3 th\'e0nh c\'f4ng s\u7869? l\u7841?\f3 i th\'e0nh c\'f4ng h\'f5n. Quan tr\f4\u7885?\f3 ng h\'f5n n\'f3 gi\'fap ng\'fd\f4\u7901?i d\'f9ng c\u7843?m th\u7845?y th\u7887?a m\'e3n, tho\u7843?i m\'e1i v\'e0 d\u7877?\f3  d\'e0ng h\'f5n khi s\f4\u7917? d\u7909?ng \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng c\u7911?a b\u7841?n.\par
